      "content": "It's natural to feel overwhelmed by such thoughts. While the future is indeed vast and unknowable, find meaning in the present. Your experiences and efforts contribute to the richness of life and to the legacy you create. Let's take one moment at a time, working to make each day matter beyond our own lives.",
      "source": "target",
